history.content:
Join us as our students from the DeCal and the club project teams show off what they have worked on this past semester and demo their cool VR applications! There will be pizza and Windows Mixed Reality headset raffles; come for a chance to win a headset while enjoying our VR projects! Spread the word - everyone is welcome, regardless of membership in the club!

Date: May 4th, 2022 (Wednesday)

Time: 5-7PM PST

Location: Cal Esports Community Center

RSVP here: https://www.facebook.com/events/1210983629707302/
history.subject: XR@B is hosting an end-of-semester showcase!
